item.title: [help] seeds [help]
item.dc:creator: @SilentCJ SilentCJ
item.description:
@SilentCJ wrote:

Yeahhh, some jackass overwrote the model files for all the seeds in the cache which is the most popular today, there is no real way to fix it, i have tried in the past, and failed, when you try and re add the models, it is not possible to make them re stackable again.
The only way you could really fix this is get an original undamaged 317 cache, and then add all your silab items back, being careful not to once again overwrite the models, to do this, i suggest renaming all your models in your models folder to a number between 10,000 and 15,000, as this is where no 317 model data is stored.

Read full topic
